126
00:07:58,420 --> 00:08:00,460
it turned out to be the zero.

127
00:08:01,990 --> 00:08:06,060
Arashiyama's answer sheet was, without a doubt, an attempt on my life.

128
00:08:07,140 --> 00:08:11,940
This was clearly a plan to commit murder!

129
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,820
No!

130
00:08:14,550 --> 00:08:18,720
