142
00:08:52,870 --> 00:08:57,010
There's no reason why we couldn't have a 20+ year old high school detective girl.

143
00:08:59,900 --> 00:09:02,390
Let's have some lessons to avoid that.

144
00:09:02,660 --> 00:09:04,600
Now, solve the problem.

145
00:09:06,660 --> 00:09:07,360
Good.

146
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,110
