149
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:19,650
Do you know how this iron ball got into the house?

150
00:09:21,470 --> 00:09:24,290
This has all the necessary information, right?

151
00:09:24,580 --> 00:09:25,960
Absolutely!

152
00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:31,650
The diameter of the ball is fixed at all angles.

153
00:09:32,220 --> 00:09:37,270
Next to it, the sides of the rectangle are also all fixed in length.

154
00:09:37,620 --> 00:09:41,690
Given this, the ball shouldn't be able to pass through the narrow door.

155
00:09:41,910 --> 00:09:43,060
This is impossible.

156
00:09:47,110 --> 00:09:48,890
You see, the answer is...

157
00:09:48,890 --> 00:09:50,940
the ball wasn't put through the door,

158
00:09:51,500 --> 00:09:54,070
but rather the house was built around the iron ball!

159
00:09:55,080 --> 00:10:00,380
It's important to think outside of the box like this in real life.

160
00:10:00,530 --> 00:10:05,830
