190
00:11:41,040 --> 00:11:45,080
We've had nothing but shameless teachers till yesterday...

191
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,940
Mr. Moriaki is a true model of a teacher!

192
00:11:47,430 --> 00:11:53,420
He was so moved that the letter still hangs in the principal's office to this day.

193
00:11:54,060 --> 00:11:55,400
And everyone lived happily ever after.

194
00:11:55,560 --> 00:11:57,520
